reviewText: On time delivery. Tons of great rides and locations. Only tweaking the picture quality somewhat would make this a five stars rating.
All the best of the 70's single fin era , soul surfing and style. A must have collection in your surf movie library.
excellent movies/ golden era /fantastic soundtracks/ hal jepsen captured a magical time

very cheesy covers, copy paper fell off when unwrapped,  looks like someone made it in their garage, dvd's are not that clear, must be a copy of a copy of a copy. Does not do Hal Jepsen justice. I  Will not buy from this vendor again.
